Fourth Department,

October, 1940.

(October 2, 1940.) Hubert J. Gillette, Trustee of John H. Warren, Bankrupt, Appellant, v. John H. Warren and Clare A. Warren, Respondents.

Orders affirmed, with ten dollars costs and disbursements. All concur. (The order and the resettled order grant a motion of defendant Clare A. Warren to examine a third party before trial.) Present — Crosby, P. J., Cunningham, Dowling, Harris and McCum, JJ.
